author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Innofactor Q4 Preliminary EBITDA At About EUR 0.7 Million​
text:
Feb 6 (Reuters) - INNOFACTOR PLC:
* REG-INNOFACTOR’S OPERATING MARGIN (EBITDA) FOR THE FOURTH QUARTER OF 2017 (Q4) IS LESS THAN EXPECTED IN THE INTERIM REPORT FOR THE THIRD QUARTER (Q3) OF 2017
* ‍OUTLOOK PUBLISHED FOR 2017 REMAINS UNCHANGED​ * ‍PRELIMINARY FIGURE FOR OPERATING MARGIN (EBITDA) FOR Q4 OF 2017 (Q4) IS APPROXIMATELY EUR 0.7 MILLION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
